      <abstract>
        <p>Silver prices fall sharply amid concern about rising United States inventories; silver for Dec delivery falls 18.8 cents, to $4.664 an ounce; graphs; table of other commodities prices (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SILVER FALLS.  Silver prices fell sharply amid concern about rising United States inventories even before the holiday jewelry-making period ends. In New York, silver for December delivery fell 18.8 cents, to $4.664 an ounce.</p>
      </block>
